# NOTE on ${POSTGRES_PASSWORD}: Synapse does not expand env vars in YAML by itself.
# Either (a) hardcode the password here (file is gitignored + chmod 600), or
# (b) run with `SYNAPSE_CONFIG_DIR` + envsubst at boot. Simplest: paste the literal
# password here and keep this file out of git (it already is via compose/.gitignore).
